<span id="freeTextContainer1931472728551653584"><strong>Good captivating story.</strong><br/><br/>Author is good story teller, but she must separate her romance novels from mystery/thrillers. Don&apos;t like to read detailed sex scenes in my thrillers. Many authors knows this and just leave the reader to fill the details.<br/>Mental illness, sexual predators needs help, not be protected by the family members.</span>
  <span id="freeText1931472728551653584" style="display:none"><strong>Good captivating story.</strong><br /><br />Author is good story teller, but she must separate her romance novels from mystery/thrillers. Don't like to read detailed sex scenes in my thrillers. Many authors knows this and just leave the reader to fill the details.<br />Mental illness, sexual predators needs help, not be protected by the family members.</span>
